# Commands

- `make install`: Install dependencies (uses --legacy-peer-deps)
- `make lint`: Run ESLint checks
- `make lint-fix`: Run ESLint with auto-fix
- `make format-check`: Check formatting with Prettier
- `make format`: Format code with Prettier
- `make type-check`: Run TypeScript type checking
- `make validate-all`: Run all validation checks (lint + format + type-check + security)
- `npm test` or `vitest run`: Run unit tests
- `npm run test:watch` or `vitest`: Run tests in watch mode
- `make run-standalone`: Start local development server
- `make build-standalone`: Build standalone application
